1
00:00:40,240 --> 00:00:40,920
This month,

2
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:42,960
there've been so many accidents,

3
00:00:43,159 --> 00:00:44,520
all concentrated on Aimin Street.

4
00:00:45,320 --> 00:00:46,000
Hello.

5
00:00:46,159 --> 00:00:47,479
Factory Office Secretariat here.

6
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:50,119
This is bad.

7
00:00:50,359 --> 00:00:51,320
Hello, Factory Office.

8
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:55,640
I've been exposed.

9
00:00:56,079 --> 00:00:57,000
I need a clean up.

10
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:43,120
Who are you people?

11
00:01:43,719 --> 00:01:44,920
Do you know who I am?

12
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,879
Why are you tying her up?

13
00:01:51,439 --> 00:01:52,120
Where are you going?

14
00:01:53,319 --> 00:01:54,239
To clean up.

15
00:01:56,159 --> 00:01:56,640
Hold on.

16
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,359
He's going with you.

17
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:01,200
I'm used to working alone.

18
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,079
That's an order.

19
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,799
So you're Liu Tianqi.

20
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,080
You're my idol!

21
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,439
Let's swap notes later, yeah?

22
00:02:19,439 --> 00:02:20,240
Secretary Jiao.

23
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,199
I just can't figure it out.

24
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,960
Why is Boss Long stirring up so much trouble?

25
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,840
I mean, everyone's moved out.

26
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,400
Is the land still worth anything?

27
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:29,960
Reportedly,

28
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:33,159
recent frequent accidents on Aimin Street

29
00:02:33,159 --> 00:02:35,520
have caused many residents to move away.

30
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:37,319
The cause is under investigation.

31
00:02:37,319 --> 00:02:39,680
Our reporter will keep you updated.

32
00:02:40,439 --> 00:02:41,680
What rotten luck.

33
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:43,400
Isn't this all Brother Hai's territory?

34
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:45,919
Now property values on Aimin Street

35
00:02:46,159 --> 00:02:47,879
have totally tanked.

36
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:49,360
I'm just saying,

37
00:02:49,759 --> 00:02:51,919
can't you wish Brother Hai well?

38
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:01,199
Secretary Jiao, that chick inside

39
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,560
is pretty good-looking.

40
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,159
Let us have some fun.

41
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,280
Do whatever you want.

42
00:03:06,919 --> 00:03:07,800
I'm taking off.

43
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,719
Sounds disgusting.

44
00:03:09,719 --> 00:03:11,080
No problem, Secretary Jiao.

45
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:15,319
You three, stand guard.

46
00:03:15,319 --> 00:03:16,360
I'll have some fun first.

47
00:03:17,599 --> 00:03:18,960
Listen up, people inside!

48
00:03:19,719 --> 00:03:21,360
You are surrounded!

49
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:24,360
Drop your weapons immediately!

50
00:03:26,719 --> 00:03:28,400
Boss, what do we do now?

51
00:03:28,599 --> 00:03:30,520
What do you mean what do we do? We fight!

52
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,039
I...

53
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,039
Hand over the hostage now!

54
00:03:35,719 --> 00:03:37,120
You're surrounded!

55
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:39,919
Zhu Yihai!

56
00:03:39,919 --> 00:03:40,960
I'll get you out of here!

57
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:42,000
Follow me.

58
00:03:46,039 --> 00:03:47,360
Boss, let's just surrender.

59
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,400
Don't you dare.

60
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,719
I'll go down first.

61
00:03:56,719 --> 00:03:57,680
I'll catch you at the bottom.

62
00:04:03,159 --> 00:04:03,960
Hurry up!

63
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,479
I... I'm too scared!

64
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:06,080
I'll catch you!

65
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:06,960
I'll catch you!

66
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,000
Boss, those are gunshots!

67
00:04:09,199 --> 00:04:11,199
Go grab that woman inside as a hostage!

68
00:04:11,199 --> 00:04:11,800
Okay, okay.

69
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,000
They're all coming!

70
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,199
Hurry!

71
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:19,839
I'll carry you.

72
00:04:22,759 --> 00:04:23,839
How much do you weigh?

73
00:04:23,839 --> 00:04:24,240
You...

74
00:04:26,319 --> 00:04:27,000
Boss, this is bad!

75
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:27,800
That woman got away!

76
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,480
What do we do now?

77
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,680
What do you mean what do we do?

78
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,720
Surrender, of course.

79
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:44,240
It's okay.

80
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:45,240
It's okay.

81
00:04:46,399 --> 00:04:47,600
What... what is this?

82
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,720
What's going on?

83
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,040
Secretary Jiao!

84
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:06,920
What are you doing here?

85
00:05:07,439 --> 00:05:08,480
Boss Long said

86
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,720
we can't be careless about this.

87
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:14,319
Don't worry, leave it to me. No problem.

88
00:05:50,839 --> 00:05:51,600
Wei Wei.

89
00:05:55,319 --> 00:05:57,079
You sure can fight, kid.

90
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:57,959
Move again, I dare you.

91
00:05:58,399 --> 00:05:59,759
You brought a knife too?

92
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:02,199
Good thing Dahai knew all along

93
00:06:02,199 --> 00:06:03,360
that you two would come.

94
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:09,160
Wei Wei, time's tight. Listen to me.

95
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:12,519
You and Dali, get to Huilian's place now.

96
00:06:12,519 --> 00:06:13,639
And tell Dao Balian.

97
00:06:13,639 --> 00:06:15,000
Have him bring plenty of men.

98
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,759
Where'd you two get such nerve?

99
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,680
Daring to bully my Huilian.

100
00:06:19,959 --> 00:06:20,519
Huilian.

101
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:21,759
Don't worry.

102
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:23,160
I'm here.

103
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,959
Take them to the police station.

104
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:29,600
Useless except for screwing things up.

105
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,759
Where you off to?

106
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:37,120
What happened to being together forever?

107
00:06:38,079 --> 00:06:39,040
What's wrong?

108
00:06:39,759 --> 00:06:40,720
Why the rush?

109
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,240
Run into some trouble?

110
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:43,879
What do you guys want?

111
00:06:43,879 --> 00:06:45,560
What could we possibly want?

112
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,399
Just here for a little chat.

113
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,560
Don't rush off.

114
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:50,120
Yeah, exactly.

115
00:06:50,519 --> 00:06:53,040
Whatever the trouble is, we'll help fix it.

116
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:53,920
Go on, spill it.

117
00:07:02,759 --> 00:07:03,560
Yihai,

118
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:05,399
Please, save me!

119
00:07:06,639 --> 00:07:08,199
Long Xiao forced me to do it all.

120
00:07:09,079 --> 00:07:11,920
Since Ge Zhendong gave you Aimin Street,

121
00:07:12,879 --> 00:07:14,680
Long Xiao's been dying to get rid of you.

122
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:18,360
He had Liu Tianqi sneak into Ge Zhendong's

123
00:07:18,879 --> 00:07:19,920
office and steal the public funds.

124
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:23,560
Then Liu Tianqi gave all the money to me

125
00:07:24,079 --> 00:07:25,600
so I could frame you for it.

126
00:07:27,399 --> 00:07:28,600
But I really didn't expect

127
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:30,839
that day it'd be Xiong Dali, not you.

128
00:07:31,319 --> 00:07:32,879
Then thank goodness for Dali.

129
00:07:33,279 --> 00:07:35,560
Without him, wouldn't I be in jail now?

130
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,800
If you had really gone to jail,

131
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,040
I would've surrendered

132
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,800
to make sure the truth came out.

133
00:07:40,839 --> 00:07:41,600
Zhu Yihai.

134
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:44,079
Quite the charmer, aren't you?

135
00:07:44,439 --> 00:07:46,079
Listen to her yapping away.

136
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:47,639
Everything I said is true!

137
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:50,079
Back then, to pay off my family's debt...

138
00:07:50,519 --> 00:07:52,399
Later, Long Xiao bought my freedom.

139
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,480
I had no choice but to work for him.

140
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:57,160
I never want to go back to that life.

141
00:07:57,519 --> 00:07:58,959
After meeting you, I started thinking,

142
00:07:59,759 --> 00:08:01,600
if you were the one who saved me,

143
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,680
instead of Long Xiao,

144
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:06,199
would my fate have been different?

145
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,399
Jiao Jing,

146
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,120
Repent and be saved.

147
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:15,959
Alright, sis.

148
00:08:16,199 --> 00:08:17,040
Say no more.

149
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,480
Take me away with you.

150
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:27,199
I'll find a way to explain things for you.

151
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,000
That's great!

152
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:31,759
Jiao Jing, don't move!

153
00:08:31,759 --> 00:08:32,720
Put down the knife!

154
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,279
Nobody move!

155
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:36,279
This blade doesn't have eyes!

156
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,480
I'm warning you, don't do anything stupid!

157
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,440
I don't have a choice anymore.

158
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,120
Jiao Jing!

159
00:08:41,639 --> 00:08:43,480
Didn't you say you didn't want your old life?

160
00:08:43,879 --> 00:08:44,960
I can save you.

161
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,039
I can take you away.

162
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,360
But you can't lie to me anymore.

163
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:49,720
Take me away?

164
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,440
Where would you take me?

165
00:08:51,759 --> 00:08:53,279
I don't have a home anymore.

166
00:08:53,799 --> 00:08:55,039
Without Long Xiao,

167
00:08:55,679 --> 00:08:57,519
I'm just a wandering ghost.

168
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:58,879
I can understand you,

169
00:08:58,960 --> 00:08:59,759
Jiao Jing.

170
00:09:00,559 --> 00:09:01,919
But the one Long Xiao wants is me,

171
00:09:01,919 --> 00:09:02,759
not her.

172
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,919
Let her go, alright?

173
00:09:07,399 --> 00:09:08,759
Aw, she's worried about you.

174
00:09:10,039 --> 00:09:11,879
What I can't have,

175
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,720
you won't get either.

176
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:20,559
You're insane!

177
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:22,200
Didn't I tell you?

178
00:09:22,399 --> 00:09:23,799
Don't do anything stupid!

179
00:09:23,799 --> 00:09:24,639
Yihai!

180
00:09:25,799 --> 00:09:26,559
Yihai!

181
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,240
Yihai!

182
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,360
Hold on!

183
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,200
Yihai!

184
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,240
Yihai, hold on!

185
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:35,480
Hold on, you have to hold on!

186
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,679
You have to hold on!

187
00:09:38,279 --> 00:09:39,759
Doctor, I have Type AB blood!

188
00:09:39,759 --> 00:09:40,759
Does he need a transfusion?

189
00:09:40,759 --> 00:09:42,279
Into the OR, prep for transfusion.

190
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:44,120
Yihai, hold on!

191
00:09:45,919 --> 00:09:46,759
You'll be okay.

192
00:09:47,639 --> 00:09:48,440
Come on, hurry!

